Steps:

1) install wireguard
2) enable ip forwarding
3) create subnet for clients
4) create routing rules on host
5) create routing rules on router


# https://lwn.net/Articles/748582/

    # ip link add wg0 type wireguard
    # ip addr add 10.0.0.1/24 wg0
    # wg set wg0 private-key <private-key-file>
    # ip link set wg0 up




# https://www.wireguard.com/quickstart/

